[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. BaseParser.java: Correct misplaced skipSpaces insertion and restore [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparseCOSDictionary  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Revert the erroneous replacement of the `parseCOSDictionary` method [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msignature. Re-insert the original signature and opening brace:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        protected COSDictionary [0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mboolean isDirect[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Remove the stray block brace [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that now follows the malformed [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mskipSpaces insertion.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Introduce `[0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` as a standalone utility method—insert it immediately[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore `[0m[1;35mskipWhiteSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, alongside other whitespace helpers. For example, after [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionaryNameValuePair[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` methods,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madd:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        protected void [0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            long skipped = 0L;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            final long MAX_SKIP_BYTES = 5L * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            int b;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mb = [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m && [0m[1;35misWhitespace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++skipped > MAX_SKIP_BYTES[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Too many whitespace bytes skipped [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mskipped + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mb != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35msource.unread[0m[1;39m([0m[39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Ensure all calls to `[0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` within `parseCOSDictionary`, `readString`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand other parsing routines now resolve to this newly inserted method.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Verify that the class-level braces are balanced: there must be exactly one [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatching closing brace for every method and the class itself.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. BruteForceParser.java: Preserve brace structure while enforcing maxScan  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Restore the original `do [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset < lastEOFMarker && [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m![0m[1;35mparser.isEOF[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` loop.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Extend its condition to honor `maxScan`, without removing the closing [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msemicolon or misplacing braces. Replace the trailing loop condition line with:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset < lastEOFMarker && ![0m[1;35mparser.isEOF[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && currentOffset [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<= maxScan[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Alternatively [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif readability is preferred[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, inside the loop body as its [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfirst statement add:[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset > maxScan[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            break;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      then leave the `do…[0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset < lastEOFMarker && ![0m[1;35mparser.isEOF[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munchanged.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Remove the incorrect `while [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!endOfObjFound && currentOffset <= maxScan[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheader and any extra braces introduced by the previous patch.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Confirm that after the loop’s closing semicolon, the subsequent `if [0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m …[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m[39m` block and the method’s closing brace remain in place—and that no code has been [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstranded outside the class body.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Validate other patched files  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure the entry-count guard in `PDFXrefStreamParser.java` and the [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion-depth guard in `COSParser.java` are intact and correctly enclosed within [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtheir respective methods.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Check that no unmatched braces were introduced in those files as part of the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlast patch.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Compile and test  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run `git apply --check` on the updated diff to pre-validate syntax.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild the project to confirm that all “illegal start of expression” and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m“class, interface, or enum expected” errors are resolved.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re-run the fuzzer to verify that the new `maxScan`, `[0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion-depth checks still mitigate pathological PDFs without altering existing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness or test behavior.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Restoring the original `parseCOSDictionary` signature and method body eliminates [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe stray code block that caused BaseParser’s syntax errors.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inserting `[0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in the correct utility section preserves the original [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing logic while bounding whitespace skipping.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Modifying the existing do–while loop in BruteForceParser to include `maxScan` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mrather than wholesale replacing it with a malformed while[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m keeps the class’s brace[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstructure intact.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This approach addresses the immediate compile failures without touching fuzzer [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharnesses, external dependencies, or test code, and retains the intended guard [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic from the previous patch.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Potential side effects [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., skipped spaces limit or scan limit triggering[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremain controlled and explicit; existing functionality and tests remain unaffected.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m tightened the loop condition in `BruteForceParser`. After applying this patch, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe build fails with over [0m[1;36m80[0m[39m compiler errors in `BaseParser.java`, mostly “illegal [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstatements.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A new private method `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionaryNameValuePair[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSDictionary obj[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogging on empty keys or bad values, bounds-checking for integer values, and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmarking values as direct before insertion.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Replaced the original `[0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` implementation with a new version that:  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Counts skipped whitespace bytes  [0m                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Changed the do/while condition to `while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset < lastEOFMarker && [0m    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                  [35m/[0m[35m/[0m [1;36m37[0m is the % character, a comment                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -        [1;35mwhile[0m[1m([0m [1;35misWhitespace[0m[1m([0mc[1m)[0m || c == [1;36m37[0m[1m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -        [1m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -            if [1m([0m c == [1;36m37[0m [1m)[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +        while [1m([0m[1;35misWhitespace[0m[1m([0mc[1m)[0m || c == [1;36m37[0m[1m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +        [1m{[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +            if [1m([0m++skipped > MAX_SKIP_BYTES[1m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +            [1m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                throw new [1;35mIOException[0m[1m([0m[32m"Too many whitespace bytes skipped [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m +      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         skipped + [32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1m)[0m;                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +            [1m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +            if [1m([0mc == [1;36m37[0m[1m)[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                      [1m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                          [35m/[0m[35m/[0m skip past the comment section                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                          c = [1;35msource.read[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m;                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -                [1;35mwhile[0m[1m([0m![1;35misEOL[0m[1m([0mc[1m)[0m && c != [1;36m-1[0m[1m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                while [1m([0m![1;35misEOL[0m[1m([0mc[1m)[0m && c != [1;36m-1[0m[1m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                          [1m{[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                    if [1m([0m++skipped > MAX_SKIP_BYTES[1m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                    [1m{[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                        throw new [1;35mIOException[0m[1m([0m[32m"Too many whitespace bytes skipped [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m([0m[32m"[0m + skipped + [32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1m)[0m;                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                    [1m}[0m                                                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                          [1m}[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                      [1m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Patch [33mResult[0m===                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===[33mIssue[0m===                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mReport[0m===                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         # Evaluation Report                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Summary                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The project’s libFuzzer harness reported a timeout when exercising the PDF parsing  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         code. To address potential infinite loops in whitespace skipping and object         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         searching, a developer removed an old `[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m` method and    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         introduced a new `[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m` method in `BaseParser.java`, as well as tweaks to   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         the loop structure in `BruteForceParser.java`. When the patch was applied, the      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         build of `pdfbox` failed with over [1;36m100[0m compilation errors—primarily “illegal start  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         of type” and “class, interface, or enum expected”—indicating a syntax or            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         brace‐balancing issue in `BaseParser.java` [1m([0mand cascading errors throughout the     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         rest of the class[1m)[0m.                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Description                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m. Initial Issue                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            • **Error from fuzzer:** `ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            • **Context:** The harness repeatedly exercises parsing routines in `BaseParser` [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         and `BruteForceParser` and appears to hang or run excessively long, triggering the  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         fuzzer’s timeout.                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m. Observations in the Initial Issue                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            • The timeout suggests a potential infinite loop or very long processing path,   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         likely around whitespace skipping or object‐search loops.                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            • No immediate stack trace or exception; only the fuzzer’s timeout signal.       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m. Patch Attempt                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            A. In `BaseParser.java` around line [1;36m326[0m:                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            • Removed the entire private method `[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m`.             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            • Inserted a new protected method:                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ```java                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              protected void [1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m throws IOException [1m{[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                  long skipped = 0L;                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                  final long MAX_SKIP_BYTES = 5L * [1;36m1024[0m * [1;36m1024[0m;                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                  int b;                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                  while [1m([0m[1m([0mb = [1;35msource.read[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m[1m)[0m != [1;36m-1[0m && [1;35misWhitespace[0m[1m([0mb[1m)[0m[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                      if [1m([0m++skipped > MAX_SKIP_BYTES[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                          throw new [1;35mIOException[0m[1m([0m[32m"Too many whitespace bytes skipped [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m +      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         skipped + [32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1m)[0m;                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                      [1m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                  [1m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                  if [1m([0mb != [1;36m-1[0m[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                      [1;35msource.rewind[0m[1m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1m)[0m;                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                  [1m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              [1m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              ```                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            B. In `BruteForceParser.java` around line [1;36m202[0m and again near line [1;36m246[0m:           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            • Encapsulated the object‐search loop in a new method `[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m`.    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            • Added variables `originOffset`, `currentOffset`, `maxScan`, `lastObjectId` and [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         adjusted the `do…while` condition to bound scanning by `lastEOFMarker`.             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m. Compilation Failure After Patch                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            • Maven compilation logged ~[1;36m100[0m errors, all of the form:                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              - “illegal start of type”                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              - “\[1m<[0m[1;95midentifier[0m[39m\> expected”  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - “class, interface, or enum expected”  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • The first reported error is at `BaseParser.java:[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m352[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m21[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`, indicating a syntax[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproblem at or just after the insertion point of `[0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • Subsequent errors span hundreds of lines in `BaseParser.java`, implying that a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbrace or method boundary was misplaced, causing the compiler to interpret large [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mswaths of code as top‐level declarations.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • **BaseParser.java**  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Verify that `[0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is declared within the class body, not nested [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minside another method or outside all methods.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Check matching of opening/closing braces around the patch hunk at line [0m[1;36m326[0m[39m. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Confirm that any removed code [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m did not [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mleave behind unbalanced braces or dangling comments.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • **BruteForceParser.java**  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Ensure the new `[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method has proper method signature, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbraces, and does not break existing class structure.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Validate that the modified `do…while` loop and accompanying conditionals [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrectly open and close.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • **Overall Class Structure**  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Run a lightweight syntax check [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `javac -Xlint`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m on each modified file [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto pinpoint the first unbalanced brace.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     – Review surrounding code context in both files to ensure the patch hull [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mboundaries align with the existing indentation and brace style.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo assumptions are made here about the root cause of the fuzzer timeout beyond the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobservations; this report focuses strictly on the initial error, the developer’s [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch attempt, the compilation outcome, and the specific locations and code regions[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrequiring careful review.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Revert the misplaced skipSpaces insertion and restore [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Undo the deletion of the original private boolean [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines ~[0m[1;36m339[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m375[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the newly inserted protected [0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m at line [0m[1;36m326[0m[39m; that duplicate [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethod caused a second method with the same name and unbalanced braces.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This restores the original brace structure and eliminates the “illegal start [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof type” cascade.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Merge the enhanced skip‐limit logic into the existing skipSpaces implementation:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Locate the only [0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround lines [0m[1;36m1319[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m1343[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduce a long `skipped` counter and a `MAX_SKIP_BYTES` constant at the top [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof that method.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Each time you consume a byte—whether whitespace or inside a comment—increment [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`skipped`. If `skipped` exceeds `MAX_SKIP_BYTES` [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m5[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, throw an IOException.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserve the existing comment‐skipping logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39mon ‘%’[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m exactly as before.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - At the end, rewind the last non‐skipped byte as currently implemented.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Augment readUntilEndOfCOSDictionary to guard against pathological inputs:[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Inside the while loop of [0m[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add a local `long [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mskipped = 0L;` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor a field[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and increment on each byte read.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If `skipped` exceeds the same `MAX_SKIP_BYTES`, either throw an IOException or[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreturn true [0m[1;39m([0m[39mto abort recovery[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, preventing infinite loops in corrupted [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdictionaries.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This keeps parseCOSDictionary’s recovery semantics intact while bounding its [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mruntime.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Verify parseCOSDictionary still calls the recovery method:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure lines [0m[1;36m308[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m315[0m[39m remain unchanged, so invalid dictionaries still invoke [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and react on its boolean result.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Correct BruteForceParser’s bfSearchForObjects placement and braces:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm `[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is declared at class scope [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot inside another [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethod[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure its opening `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m` at line ~[0m[1;36m202[0m[39m has a matching closing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` before the next[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethod or class closing brace.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify the `do…while` loops inside it are properly closed, and the `if` blocks[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maround `lastEOFMarker` and `lastObjOffset` remain within the method.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Compile and smoke‐test:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run `mvn compile -q`; errors in BaseParser should clear.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re‐run the libFuzzer harness to ensure no infinite‐loop issues persist.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All existing unit tests and parsing functionality must pass unchanged.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- By restoring the original recovery method and merging skip‐limit logic into a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msingle skipSpaces, we avoid duplicate methods and brace misalignment, resolving the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msyntax errors.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Integrating the byte‐cap counter into both [0m[1;35mskipSpaces[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mreadUntilEndOfCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m addresses the original timeout—bounding whitespace [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mskipping and dictionary recovery—without altering harness or fuzzing logic.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This approach preserves existing parsing behavior [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhitespace/comment skipping [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand dictionary recovery[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, keeps method signatures unchanged, and ensures [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munobtrusive fixes that won’t break downstream tests or the public API. [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
